'''Julaire "Julie" Andelin''' is a native of [[wikipedia:Salt Lake City|Salt Lake City, Utah]], and the current co-chair of [http://www.mountaincon.org/about.html Mountain-Con], an annual science fiction and fantasy fandom celebration in Utah. She contributed some entries to the ''[[J.R.R. Tolkien Encyclopedia: Scholarship and Critical Assessment]]''.
